Purpose:
Network issues are among the most common problems faced by DevOps engineers.

Ping:
Check connectivity to a host.
ping google.com

Traceroute:
Find the network path.
traceroute google.com

DNS Lookup:
nslookup google.com

Dig Command:
dig google.com

Check Listening Ports:
ss -tulpn
Test Specific Port
telnet google.com 443

Real-Time Scenario:
Application is inaccessible.
Troubleshooting Steps:

ping server-ip
ss -tulpn
systemctl status nginx
curl localhost
